Implement ProjectFileSet: owns TempDir, HashMap<PathBuf, Vec<u8>>, tracks root vs dependency. FileCommand trait with apply()/undo(). ModifyCommand and ExcludeCommand implementations. Per-file command stack. from_directory(path, roots): recursive load, skip .git/ target/ etc, classify root/dep. update_file(): push ModifyCommand. exclude_file(): push ExcludeCommand, error on roots. undo_last(): pop and undo. root_files(), dependency_files() (sorted by size desc), temp_dir_path(). See multi-file spec "Project File Set".
